Dad seems pretty busy talking
with the people from the Chamber
of Commerce at the moment.

rows.label: tlk70000005_02_msg0002

I've got to do my bit here,
pulling the customers in.
That's my lookout.

rows.label: tlk70000005_02_msg0003

It's not so bad though,
with Joey around.
